The location allows easy access from major nearby road and rail transport facilities, as well as benefitting from the multitude of nearby retail, food eateries, medical surgeries, childcare, fitness centres and other social facilities.

Key features of the Premises include:

•	Fitted out office space
•	Floor to ceiling glass facade
•	North Facing Aspect
•	Security controlled building
•	Kitchenette
•	4 parking spaces
•	Extensive district views

For further information or to arrange an inspection contact the exclusive CBRE agents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to offer A Grade office space for lease in one of Norwest’s landmark office buildings. Vantage offers exceptional corporate appeal for all businesses both small and large with an attractive glass façade spanning over 5 levels. Located in an advantageous position offering ease of access to both major arterial roads and Bella Vista Metro. 

Vantage benefits from the following key features;
-	Corporate office work environment
-	Extensive district views
-	Marble reception lobby 
-	Building serviced by 4 lifts
-	Proximity to social, retail and leisure amenity 

Available Suites:
Level 4 (Whole floor) – 2,722.5sqm – Open plan floor area
Level 3 (Suite 1) – 1,521.5sqm – Partially fitted out 
Level 3 (Suite 2) – 607sqm – to be subdivided with speculative fit outs from 230sqm
Level 2 (Suite 3) – 530sqm – Fitted out 
Basement 1 – 251sqm – Partially fit out

- Potential to combine level 3 and 4 for a total tenancy of 4,851sqm. 

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive agents Mark Martin on 0412 699 662 or Anthony Forcella on 0434 035 628.
